{
  "stem": "11801.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we asked them to-- to use the money for whatever they wanted to buy, television sets or you know, buy some new furniture.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they just refused.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They said they would put it in-- place it in his account.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We-- we, of course, have no idea what happened to the money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know, I personally don't care.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But I think it's incredible that, you know, a little country like Belgium, population of 10 million, you know, has-- has the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] has the ability and the heart to look after children who come from other places, come from other countries, and treat them like one of their own.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, a few years ago, it was interesting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they take them on trips three or four times a year.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they take them on shorter trips.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They go on mini trips.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Day trips they do all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But three or four times a year, they take them for five or six days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They take them to the seashore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They take them to interesting cities in Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a few years ago, they were going to Eastern Europe, I believe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the-- when we were there, they told us that they wouldn't take him, because they were afraid, because he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they're very aware of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, there is-- I have an incredible story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A-- a dentist from Antwerp, a very, very Orthodox Jew, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, I don't know, maybe 10, 15 years ago, was researching [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some records to find out if anyone needed help from him.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In other words, he was looking to do some good deeds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, this is very important to the Orthodox, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
